{
  "stem": "2533.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is the Regina Zielinski.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's R-E-G-I-N-A, and Zielinski is Z-I-E-L-I-N-S-K-I.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my maiden name is Feldman, F-E-L-D-M-A-N.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The 2nd to 9, September, 1925.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In another few months, it will be 70.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a small town between two big cities, between Lublin and Chelm and was called Siedliszcze.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it is S-I-E-D-L-I-S-Z-C-Z-E.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poland.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and Chelm, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- buses used to run to Chelm and Lublin because the railway station was a little bit too far away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was only 51 kilometers to Lublin and 24 to Chelm, but different directions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's name was Joseph, and my mother's, Golda-- pardon me-- and, how shall I say, a Jewish home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were living on the outskirts of the town because my father had a building business-- building material business, and we were so integrated between the-- the Catholics and the Lutheranians and the-- the-- the Seventh-day Adventists.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had only one very big school, and there was a-- a Orthodox-- Russian Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were all in the same school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a primary school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was sometime, I think, about a thousands kids in that school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The school was converted after the First World War.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a castle, and the one who owned that castle and the surrounding-- surrounding, they didn't have any heirs, so they gave it to the town.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they made out a school-- school for it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a beautiful, beautiful school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't recall much till about '37, 1937.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have had heard that in bigger cities, they had pickets standing, and they had the Jewish shops.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not allowed like to go and buy from Jews and all that.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
